<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.9">
<l>tiraṇṭeḻu taḻaima ḻaimukil vaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṅkamala malarcūḻ vaṇṭiṉam pōlē</l>
<l>curuṇṭiruṇ ṭakuḻal tāḻntamu kattā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉūtukiṉ ṟakuḻa lōcaiva ḻiyē</l>
<l>maruṇṭu māṉkaṇaṅkaḷ mēykaima ṟantu</l>
<l rend="indent">mēyntapul luṅkaṭai vāyvaḻi cōra</l>
<l>viraṇṭupā ṭuntulaṅ kāppuṭai peyarā</l>
<l rend="indent">veḻutucit tiraṅkaḷ pōlaniṉ ṟaṉavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way the sound of the flute that was played</l>
<l rend="indent">by the one with the face where dark, curly hair hangs</l>
<l rend="indent">Like a group of bees that surrounds a red lotus flower,</l>
<l rend="indent">him with the hue of round, abundant, high rain clouds</l>
<l>[made] the bewildered herd of deer forget [their] grazing</l>
<l>so that the grazed grass fell from the corners of their mouths,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and], without swaying to either side, nor shifting in place,</l>
<l>They stood like embellishments on a painting.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
